# TASK 6.5 — LLM Reasoning Addon for Procedural Success Outputs

## INTENDED Footprint

Add an optional LLM-generated reasoning sentence to the SUCCESS outputs of all
procedural action paths in RMS and MRR workflows. The addon is append-only
(never replaces the deterministic message). Silent fallback on LLM failure.
Controlled by a single `ENABLE_REASONING_ADDON` feature flag.

